title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 31 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 31 2022
description:
Pennsylvania Democrat candidate John Fetterman is rolling out the "Biden Basement" campaign strategy. Let's replay the great "Biden Leg Hair" story. Unelected New York Governor Kathy Hochul declares Times Square a gun-free zone -- will criminals listen? California Governor Gavin Newsom, faces self-inflicted energy crisis, his in-laws giving money to his political rival DeSantis and will forever look like every 1980's movie villain. Elon Musk calls for more oil and gas. What are your thoughts on Eddie Murphy doing a Beverly Hills Cop part 4?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
